content:
[[include :scp-wiki-cn:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]
[[module CSS]]
h1, h2 {
    text-align: center;
}

.step_container {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    border: 1px solid #999;
    padding: 1em;
}

#page-title {
    display: none;
}

#page-content > .collapsible-block {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0.75em;
    background-color: lightgrey;
    border-top: 0.125rem dashed slategrey;
    border-bottom: 0.125rem dashed slategrey;
}

#page-content > div.collapsible-block > div.collapsible-block-unfolded > div.collapsible-block-content {
    text-align:left;
}
[[/module]]
[[>]]
[[module rate]]
[[/>]]
----
+ 轻量化异常分类栏
----
[[div class="step_container"]]
+ [/anomaly-classification-system-guide 使用前请先阅读此指南]。
++ 请先阅读[[[component:anomaly-class-bar|原版ACS指南]]]以获取更多信息。
----
[[=]]
+++ 此组件不必与黑色标记笔主题一起使用
+++ 此组件可与原版ACS同时使用[[footnote]]近期将发布一个桌面端使用原版ACS、移动端使用Lite模式的替代模块。[[/footnote]]
[[/=]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="step_container"]]
++++ 此组件由[[*user dr-hormress]]仿照[[*user woedenaz]]制作的异常分类栏（ACS）组件设计，由于组件结构是全新的，其并不兼容大部分ACS扩展组件。
[[/div]]

+ 示例

[[include component:acs-horm-lite-source
|lang= cn
|item-number= 2105
|clearance= 2
|container-class= euclid
|secondary-class= none
|disruption-class= vlam
|risk-class= 待观察
]]
@@ @@
[[include component:acs-horm-lite-source
|lang= cn
|item-number= 3000
|clearance= 5
|container-class= 机密
|secondary-class= thaumiel
|secondary-icon= http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Aanomaly-class-bar/thaumiel-icon.svg
|disruption-class= ekhi
|risk-class= 危急
]]
@@ @@
[[include component:acs-horm-lite-source
|lang= cn
|item-number= 4511
|clearance= 4
|container-class= 等待分级
|secondary-class= none
|disruption-class= none
|risk-class= none
]]

